reviewText:
If you go on the hot body website you will find the majority of the clips on that site that you have on this dvd. The reason I coughed up some extra bucks to get this dvd was that the strip scenes were meant to be longer.

No they are not. Waste of money.

I would be rating the service and not the movie.
The services was great.
The movie onn the other hand was worse then a
rejected B rate movie that was tossed on the studio floor.
